@NODE Requirements "3.1  Requirements"
@{u}@{b}3.1 Requirements@{uu}@{ub}

· Kickstart and Workbench V37 or later.
· Reqtools.library (available on Aminet).
· Memory usage is fairly low.
· ±300 kilobytes on your HD.  (Only ±20 kilobytes have to reside on your
  boot partition.)
@ENDNODE





@NODE Installation "3.2  Installation"
@{u}@{b}3.2  Installation@{uu}@{ub}
Installation is accomplished through an Installerą script.  Simply
double-click on the Install icon and follow the on-screen instructions.
Please do not install IntuiCookie by hand, it only causes unnecessary
trouble.


__________
ą Installer is © Escom AG and not included in this archive.
@ENDNODE





@NODE Usage "4.1  Usage"
@{u}@{b}4.1  Usage@{uu}@{ub}

FROM WORKBENCH

Simply start it by clicking on its icon.
A window will be opened, click on "Continue" to close it.
IntuiCookie can be customised via @{"tooltypes" LINK Tooltypes}.

FROM CLI

Simply enter IntuiCookie's name in a Shell window.  All
cookies will be output to the Shell window, but error
messages will still be displayed in Requesters and command
line options aren't supported either.

@ENDNODE



